# Configuration file for fw_(printenv/setenv) on Hi3516CV6xx.
#
# Without this file fw_printenv fails, and load_hisilicon then falls back to
# its built-in "mem_total=64" default (see files/script/load_hisilicon) — on a
# 128 MB board that silently strands half the DDR: the OS keeps its mem=64M
# and MMZ is sized as 32M instead of 64M.
#
# NOR layout comes from u-boot-hi3516cv6xx configs/hi3516cv610_openipc_defconfig:
#   CONFIG_ENV_OFFSET=0x40000, CONFIG_ENV_SIZE=0x10000, single (non-redundant) env.
# mtd0 is the 320K "boot" partition declared by the mtdparts in bootargs, so the
# env lives at 0x40000 inside it. Erase block on the SPI-NOR parts used here is
# 64K, hence the 0x10000 sector size.
#
# MTD device name   Device offset   Env. size   Flash sector size
/dev/mtd0           0x40000         0x10000     0x10000
